info.author: Kristoffer Erlandsson
info.description:
A python module that makes it possible and quite easy to write WindowMaker
dockapps using Python. It is mostly a wrapper around the good old wmgeneral.c
that has been used a long time. But some other functionality is added too.
info.name: pywmgeneral
info.summary: Python module for making WindowMaker dockapps
